	<p><strong>Economy Vinyl:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Climate performance:</strong> Adequate but shows UV damage within 5-7 years</li>
		<li><strong>Durability:</strong> 15-20 years, may yellow or chalk in intense sun</li>
		<li><strong>Maintenance:</strong> Minimal, occasional washing</li>
		<li><strong>Cost:</strong> $25-35 per linear foot installed</li>
		<li><strong>Best application:</strong> Short-term installations, rental properties</li>
	</ul>

	<p><strong>Mid-Grade Vinyl:</strong></p>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Climate performance:</strong> Good UV resistance, handles heat well</li>
		<li><strong>Durability:</strong> 20-25 years with consistent appearance</li>
		<li><strong>Maintenance:</strong> Annual washing, inspect fasteners annually</li>
		<li><strong>Cost:</strong> $30-45 per linear foot installed</li>
		<li><strong>Best application:</strong> Most residential privacy fence applications</li>
	</ul>

	<p><strong>Premium Vinyl:</strong></p>
